# Dev workflow (padel exam app)

## Encoding

All files under `app/` must be **UTF-8**. Latin-1 (`0xED` for í) or Windows-1252 (`0x97` for —) breaks Nixpacks/Turbopack with `stream did not contain valid UTF-8` even when `npm run dev` works locally.

Portuguese UI strings: use literal UTF-8 (`Concluído`, `Prática`, `Năo`, em dash `—`).

## Before done

From `app/`:

1. `npm run check:utf8`
2. `npm run lint`
3. `npx tsc --noEmit`
4. `npm run build` (runs `check:utf8` via `prebuild`)

